Class PBKDF2Hasher

  • java.lang.Object
    • ml.alternet.security.auth.hashers.impl.HasherBase<WorkFactorSaltedParts>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Credentials.Checker, Hasher

    public class PBKDF2Hasher
extends HasherBase<WorkFactorSaltedParts>
    A slightly modified PBKDF2 hasher, that erase intermediate data. The underlying MAC algorithm is unchanged.
    Author:
    Philippe Poulard
